        ],
        "params": {
          "text": "# \ud83d\uded2 Retail Ops Command Center\n\nThe full tour of flograph in one canvas:\n\n1. **Sources** \u2014 five editable on-canvas tables\n2. **Enrich** \u2014 concatenate quarters, join twice, derive revenue / cost / margin\n3. **Regional** \u2014 rollup vs targets, KPI cards, HTML executive briefing\n4. **Product mix** \u2014 segment slicer, category rollup, region \u00d7 category pivot\n5. **Trend & Pareto** \u2014 monthly trend, ABC classification script\n6. **Data quality** \u2014 describe() statistics + margin distribution\n\n\u25b6 Press **F5** (Run All), then explore the **Overview / Detail / Executive** pages below.",
          "width": 640,
          "height": 0
        },
        "code": null,
        "label": null
      },
